window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Long have we been alone; without brides, without females to warm us during the long nights, without sweet mates. </b></p> <p>But we see them from afar, the brides that could be ours. Kept away from us by walls and weapons. Females we long for greatly...obsessively.<i> Human</i> females. And the one with red hair? I want her. I saw her first.</p> <p>I will fight to the death for her. She is mine. So, we’ll come together and make an exchange with their men that will benefit us all. After that? To the winner goes the spoil. Let the hunt begin...but the red-headed female is mine.</p> <p><i>Viper</i> is the first book in Naga Brides, a series about bride-hunting aliens with the charm of a snake, the wiles of the devil, and the will to do anything for their females.</p>"; 
